parcel.description: Brazilian NFT Museum and Brazucas NFT Gallery

features.text:
On your right, Brazucas NFT Gallery on KnownOrigin and the Brazilian NFT Museum have the honor to present the amazing audiovisual art of Diego Mac, Brazilian artist building a collection of Sylphides and Preludes, as his genesis pieces on Brazucas NFT. Both are series made with 3D art, with dancing human body parts, in a mandala form, making reference to the organic nature of human form. Click each Prelude and each Sylphide to watch the short movie. Do not forget to turn on the sound. Click KO symbol to go to our KO Gallery.

Curated by The Philosopher

Welcome to the Brazilian NFT Museum, by Brazucas NFT. Please, sign the guestbook, read the texts on the wall, and enjoy the exhibition. Click the works or the photos of the artists for more information. Feel free to collect the NFTs and support the artistic work of Brazilian artists. You can fly by pressing F. If you came for the mystery, talk to the Orixas.

On your right, Brazucas NFT Gallery on KnownOrigin and the Brazilian NFT Museum have the honor to present the second audiovisual Brazilian artist from our gallery, Igor Martins. He creates series of 3D art, with moving objects talking about the nature of change and permanence in the processes of our world. Click the works to have also the musical experience integated with video. His works are really mesmerizing. Click KO symbol below to go to our KO Gallery.

Curated by The Philosopher

In this room, Brazucas NFT Gallery on KnownOrigin and the Brazilian NFT Museum have the honor to present the amazing audiovisual art of the Brazilian artist Fitipe. He is building an interesting experience with nature and tech objects and glitches, that mix and blend up to the original forms are dissolved into abstract technological patterns with an organinc soul. Click each NFT to know more abour them. Do not forget to turn on the sound. Click KO symbol to go to our KO Gallery.

Curated by The Philosopher

On the right, Brazucas NFT Gallery on KnownOrigin and the Brazilian NFT Museum have the honor to present the amazing audiovisual art of NX. He has a successful history on tezos blockchain, creating 1/1 GIFs, and he is bringing his GIFs and Web3 Culture characters to KO, on ethereum blockchain. Click each NFT to know more abour them. Click KO symbol to go to our KO Gallery. While NX is preparing to enter KO, check his NFTs on tezos.

Curated by The Philosopher

A path to enlightenment is a path to oneself, a path to self awareness. Meet our twins in the Burning Ritual and ask them about the EYE. One of them can take you to Obscurity. From there, you can find your way into the Mystery. Take the teleport sphere in the tree and go up to the terrace.
Click below to check the Oncyber Gallery for Brazucas NFT III inside NFT Rio.
